00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,740
(Episode 6)
Aren't you embarrassed?

2
00:00:00,740 --> 00:00:01,740
(Episode 6)
I'm not making a big fuss.

3
00:00:01,740 --> 00:00:03,220
- Yes, you are.
- What do you know?

4
00:00:03,220 --> 00:00:04,000
He started it!

5
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,520
Kai, do something!

6
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:08,200
Enough.

7
00:00:09,060 --> 00:00:10,320
Everything...

8
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,920
