- Kai!
- Hey, Kai!

11
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:20,900
- Kai!
- Kai, are you okay?

12
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:22,240
Don't touch him yet.

13
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,340
Hey, Kai! Kai!

14
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,620
Are you alright, sir?

15
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:27,860
Hmm?

16
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,227
Ah, it's nothing.

17
00:00:30,470 --> 00:00:32,150
I'm just a bit nervous, I guess.

18
00:00:32,641 --> 00:00:33,320
Huh?

19
00:00:34,368 --> 00:00:35,320
Maybe it's that...

20
00:00:35,900 --> 00:00:37,160
the turmoil of love.

21
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:40,480
Fuma's pure heart wavered.

22
00:00:40,740 --> 00:00:42,080
Is it arrhythmia?

23
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:43,909
You've been working and

24
00:00:43,934 --> 00:00:46,019
playing harder than usual lately.

25
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:48,400
As expected. You can tell, huh?

26
00:00:49,140 --> 00:00:51,840
Well, it's not arrhythmia.

27
00:00:52,380 --> 00:00:53,692
Currently, I haven't received

28
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:54,723
