31
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:58,920
But I won't be discouraged.

32
00:00:59,448 --> 00:01:00,888
What are you talking about?

33
00:01:04,820 --> 00:01:06,820
Oh, I feel better now.

34
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:10,120
Hello? Kai-kun?

35
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:13,480
Oh, Rei?

36
00:01:16,860 --> 00:01:18,280
Got it. I'm on my way!

37
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:21,580
What are the plans after this?

38
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,260
Everything is adjustable.

39
00:01:23,915 --> 00:01:24,980
As expected of you.

40
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:30,920
I'm coming.

41
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,140
Hang on, Kai.

42
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,480
"Love in The Air -Premonition of Love-"

43
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,340
Fuma-san!

44
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:54,800
Rei! Where's Kai?!

45
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,640
He just fell asleep.

46
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,425
Don't wake him up.

47
00:02:58,433 --> 00:03:00,536
Let me explain what's going on first.

48
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,400
Fuma-san, listen to me.

49
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:08,792
Kai got dizzy and fell unconscious

50
00:03:08,816 --> 00:03:10,256
at the university.

51
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:13,159
The doctor said it was

52
00:03:13,183 --> 00:03:15,183
a psychogenic fever caused by

53
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,460
lack of sleep and excessive stress.

54
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:19,560
Stress?

55
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,242
Being a member of the

56
00:03:21,266 --> 00:03:22,437
executive committee of

57
00:03:22,453 --> 00:03:23,696
the school festival is hard work.

58
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,375
But Kai does a lot because he

59
00:03:25,391 --> 00:03:27,456
is a caring and responsible person.

60
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,200
So it's probably too much of a burden.

61
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,040
Even though I was there for him,

62
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,600
but I couldn't help him.

63
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,840
I'm the same as you.

64
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,520
He still have a fever,

65
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:49,376
and the doctor says he

66
