should really be hospitalized.

67
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:52,440
Huh?

68
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,723
He didn't want to go because

69
00:03:54,747 --> 00:03:56,535
he didn't want to worry his parents.

70
00:03:57,653 --> 00:04:00,920
I want to do the committee duties

71
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,620
