73
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,920
That's why...

74
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,300
Can I trust you?

75
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:17,520
Of course.

76
00:04:20,960 --> 00:04:22,100
I promise

77
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:24,342
I won't do anything weird

78
00:04:24,358 --> 00:04:25,558
to your friend.

79
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,890
When Kai talks about Fuma-san,

80
00:04:35,915 --> 00:04:37,672
