81
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,900
What? What's that?

82
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,080
Just take care of him.

83
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,871
If I was just playing around,

84
00:05:12,895 --> 00:05:14,207
