85
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,940
Even I'm surprised myself.

86
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,900
- Don't go.
- What's wrong? Kai?

87
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:30,980
You're sweating a lot.

88
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:32,635
I'm not going anywhere.

89
00:05:32,643 --> 00:05:33,916
Let's get you cleaned up, okay?

90
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:36,240
Don't go, please.

91
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:42,700
It's okay. I'm here.

92
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,440
No one's going to hurt you.

93
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,683
I don't want to have

94
