95
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,740
Dream?

96
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,460
Tell me, Kai.

97
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:00,140
Who's been making you feel this way?

98
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,280
Dad.

99
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:07,880
Huh?

100
00:06:10,063 --> 00:06:11,623
