101
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,380
Being mistaken for your dad?

102
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,960
Or about cursing your dad?

103
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,960
Why do you have to look so cute,

104
00:06:25,969 --> 00:06:27,171
