105
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,210
Why do your eyes always

106
00:06:32,235 --> 00:06:34,304
look like you're asking for help?

107
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:44,140
Is there anything I can do?”

108
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:08,156
Changing the bed sheet,

109
00:07:08,172 --> 00:07:09,532
wiping your body,

110
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,975
This is the first time I've done

111
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,484
something for someone else.

112
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,060
It's a first for me, really.

113
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,920
I swear.

114
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:31,940
Nope.

115
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,400
I promised Rei.

116
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,580
Laundry time.

117
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:14,720
Oh, did you wake up? Seductive boy.

118
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,240
What are you even talking about?

119
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:20,880
Huh? You don't remember?

120
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:23,840
You clung to me all night.

121
00:08:24,073 --> 00:08:24,960
Huh?

122
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,540
I didn't...

123
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,150
You don't know how much I

124
00:08:31,158 --> 00:08:32,822
endured that fierce temptation.

125
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,700
Oh, the committee work.

126
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,960
Rei is doing it for you.

127
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,560
- You have to rest now.
- But...

128
00:08:45,592 --> 00:08:46,652
No buts.

129
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:52,820
Wait a moment.

130
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:07,320
Here. A present.

131
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,540
I don't want it.

132
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,740
Do you want to know why sunflowers?

133
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:15,500
I don't want to know.

134
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:22,000
Because they face the sky.

135
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:24,140
Even if I can't be your sun,

136
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,561
I want you to look at these

137
00:09:25,586 --> 00:09:26,706
and remember that

138
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:28,844
the wind always wraps the sky

139
00:09:28,869 --> 00:09:30,194
and watches over you.

140
00:09:34,815 --> 00:09:36,035
That's so cheesy.

141
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:38,760
Alright.

142
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:40,518
Now the stubborn, selfish

143
00:09:40,543 --> 00:09:41,908
and grumpy time is over.

144
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,060
I'll make you food.

145
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,969
Please take your medicine

146
00:09:45,985 --> 00:09:47,109
and go back to bed.

147
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:12,500
Good morning.

148
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,440
It's ‘Love in the air'.

149
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,889
This morning, due to low

150
00:10:15,913 --> 00:10:17,107
atmospheric pressure,

151
00:10:17,132 --> 00:10:18,865
temperatures are spiking.

152
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:20,623
Be cautious of sudden

153
00:10:20,648 --> 00:10:21,904
strong gusts of wind.

154
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,100
- Now, here's the first track for today.
- Haa...

155
00:10:24,335 --> 00:10:25,535
"Sunflower"

156
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,260
Finally halfway there!

157
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:29,960
Don't overdo it.

158
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:32,654
Don't overdo it. If you collapse too,

159
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:33,788
we're in trouble.

160
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:36,100
Yeah. Thanks.

161
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:42,000
That's quite the workload.

162
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,472
Kai tried to handle all

163
00:10:45,488 --> 00:10:47,464
of this on his own. I can't believe it.

164
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:51,776
When he is in trouble,

165
00:10:51,863 --> 00:10:53,667
that guy doesn't really tell me.

166
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:59,180
If only I'd noticed sooner...

167
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:03,726
Sometimes we don't know

168
00:11:04,196 --> 00:11:05,876
what's in our heart.

169
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:11,740
After realizing it, just do our best.

170
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,040
Fuma is doing the same now.

171
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,980
Fuma-san...

172
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,720
I wonder if he's been kicked out?

173
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,240
Huh?

174
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,907
Kai's oblivious

175
00:11:26,932 --> 00:11:28,612
when it comes to himself.

176
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:33,940
So it's a trial for Fuma, huh?

177
00:11:35,591 --> 00:11:37,631
It would be great if he could pass.

178
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:40,920
Rei.

179
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:44,400
- Why are you worrying about others?
- Huh?

180
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:46,640
Well...

181
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:48,660
we've already

182
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:52,420
overcome it, haven't we?

183
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,840
- Not yet.
- Huh?

184
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,780
We've only done a fifth of it.

185
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,499
There's still twice

186
00:12:02,515 --> 00:12:04,382
as much material in the car.

187
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,040
You're right.

188
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:10,200
We have a long way to go.

189
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,560
But...

190
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,556
But if you get over it,

191
00:12:15,581 --> 00:12:16,962
it'll be good, right?

192
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:21,760
Let's find out. As soon as possible!

193
00:12:38,649 --> 00:12:40,007
Sorry for the wait.

194
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:43,900
Please eat.

195
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,642
I've never made it for

196
00:12:45,650 --> 00:12:47,173
my younger brother or sister,

197
00:12:48,211 --> 00:12:49,751
but it's probably alright.

198
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:01,140
I'm better now.

199
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,140
It's time for you to go home.

200
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:06,220
You know what's worse

201
00:13:06,236 --> 00:13:07,136
than a one-night stand?

202
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,298
Being discarded after being

203
00:13:08,306 --> 00:13:09,384
completely used up.

204
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,780
I spent all night taking care of you.

205
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,490
And now that I'm no longer needed,

206
00:13:18,506 --> 00:13:19,701
you're kicking me out?

207
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,053
I may be shameless,

208
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:23,826
but I'm still sensitive, you know.

209
00:13:26,060 --> 00:13:27,520
What do you want?

210
00:13:29,332 --> 00:13:30,512
You already know.

211
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,920
I won't give it to you.

212
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:38,260
I'm not going to sleep with you.

213
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,180
No matter what it is,

214
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,400
I can't give you what you want.

215
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:44,940
I see...

216
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,080
I guess you don't know after all.

217
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:52,720
Sure, I wanted to sleep with you.

218
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:55,780
But that's old news.

219
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,340
What I want now is

220
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,080
stop ignoring me.

221
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,520
Pick up the phone sometimes,

222
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,520
reply to a message here and there.

223
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,080
Don't run away when we meet.

224
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,600
And most importantly,

225
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:16,980
let me woo you.

226
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:19,880
That's all I'm asking for.

227
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:27,800
I'll back off for now.

228
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,263
But once you're fully recovered,

229
00:14:32,271 --> 00:14:33,552
you'd better be ready.

230
00:14:35,420 --> 00:14:38,060
Push all you want, I'm not interested.

231
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,473
By the way, there's some

232
00:14:43,497 --> 00:14:44,520
jelly in the fridge.

233
00:14:45,220 --> 00:14:46,320
Take care of yourself.

234
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:00,360
I don't like owing people.

235
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,680
Thanks for everything.

236
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,660
Next time, I won't let you escape.

237
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,700
You'll never catch me.

238
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:27,760
(Kaminiji University)

239
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,980
(Faculty of Engineering
Bachelor of Architecture Program)

240
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:30,240
- Sorry!
- Sorry!"

241
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,105
We relied on you way too much.

242
00:15:33,121 --> 00:15:35,128
So you pushed yourself too hard,

243
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,520
especially as your senior.

244
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,337
I'm sorry too!

245
00:15:38,361 --> 00:15:40,040
You're always helping me out.

246
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,100
Kai.

247
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:46,380
Today, you're just going to sit.

248
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,240
- Huh?
- Geez!

249
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:52,020
You need to rest and rest!

250
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:55,160
Now, everyone, let's get to work!

251
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,760
Work!

252
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,340
I'm just a burden, aren't I?

253
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,920
That's not true.

254
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,212
Because Kai has been

255
00:16:07,237 --> 00:16:08,517
working hard all along,

256
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,760
