265
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,934
If it's something important to you,

266
00:17:03,959 --> 00:17:05,129
I won't stop you.

267
00:17:06,292 --> 00:17:07,192
But...

268
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,379
I want a reward for coming

269
00:17:09,395 --> 00:17:10,504
to pick you up.

270
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:18,000
A cute smile would be enough.

271
00:17:32,660 --> 00:17:33,680
Ha!

272
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:35,680
Oh!

273
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,480
Ha!

274
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:39,740
Cha!

275
00:17:40,804 --> 00:17:41,824
Shoo!

276
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,100
Ha!

277
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,220
Ugh, you're noisy!

278
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:48,445
You're not going to leave

279
00:17:48,468 --> 00:17:49,526
