280
00:17:49,551 --> 00:17:51,331
So at least be still and be quiet!

281
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,000
Wonderful!

282
00:17:55,327 --> 00:17:56,452
You understand the heart of

283
00:17:56,477 --> 00:17:57,679
your future boyfriend.

284
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,860
Just kidding.

285
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,120
What's this?

286
00:18:27,171 --> 00:18:28,040
Whoosh.

