It's just three lines.

289
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:37,380
Why draw it on my hand?

290
00:18:37,660 --> 00:18:39,420
To mark you as mine.

291
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:41,620
Haa...

292
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:52,060
You are good at it.

293
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,700
I'm an architecture student.

294
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:57,980
Fuma-san.

295
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,820
No matter what you write,

296
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:04,020
you belong to no one

297
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,000
but yourself.

298
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:10,840
How are you not blushing after all this?

299
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:13,160
Not at all.

300
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:24,066
I want to change,

301
00:19:24,091 --> 00:19:25,691
can I borrow your clothes?

302
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,460
Mmm.

303
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:40,600
Hey Kai, have you become an idiot?

304
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:43,160
Just now you...

305
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,080
were waiting for a kiss?

306
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,240
Huh?

307
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:04,780
You're making me sleep on the floor?

308
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:08,120
You came uninvited, it can't be helped.

309
00:20:08,878 --> 00:20:10,300
Sharing a bed...

310
00:20:10,325 --> 00:20:12,019
What kind of relationship is that?

311
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:18,700
Don't come up to the bed after I sleep.

312
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,780
How untrustworthy am I?

313
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:26,880
I've been a player in the past,

314
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,655
but since sleeping with you,

315
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,249
I haven't touched anyone else.

316
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:37,020
I'm not an idiot.

317
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,300
Fine, once.

318
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,840
Twice.

319
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:48,989
Alright, three times.

320
00:20:48,998 --> 00:20:50,678
But no more, I swear!

321
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:56,400
I haven't seen anyone in two months.

322
00:20:58,747 --> 00:21:01,707
Okay. I'll listen to you this time.

323
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:05,080
This time or another time,

324
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:08,820
it's me who wins.

325
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:12,420
It can't be helped.

326
00:21:12,747 --> 00:21:14,007
I already lost.

327
00:21:15,140 --> 00:21:16,160
Goodnight.

328
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,080
What are you staring at?

329
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,500
Your palm lines?

330
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:59,030
Wanna read mine?

331
00:21:59,070 --> 00:22:00,756
Tell me about my love life!

332
00:22:00,780 --> 00:22:02,300
Skyrocketing.

333
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:04,280
Seriously?

334
00:22:04,840 --> 00:22:06,240
So annoying.

335
00:22:15,420 --> 00:22:16,480
Umm...

336
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:21,780
Do you just have endless time and money?

337
00:22:22,640 --> 00:22:23,999
Well, enough to support

338
00:22:24,024 --> 00:22:25,891
Kai for the rest of my life.

339
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:29,960
I didn't ask for it.

340
00:22:32,347 --> 00:22:33,487
If you don't eat,

341
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:36,040
you won't have energy.

342
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,120
I can do it by myself.

343
00:22:44,180 --> 00:22:45,453
If my siblings saw this,

344
00:22:45,478 --> 00:22:46,998
they'd be laughing.

345
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:49,680
You're close with them?

346
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,280
Want to know?

347
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:59,000
My brother's a third-year in college,

348
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,340
my sister's a freshman.

349
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,980
We're close, but they're stubborn,

350
00:23:04,005 --> 00:23:05,872
persistent, and troublesome.

351
00:23:06,566 --> 00:23:07,706
Being an older brother

352
00:23:07,731 --> 00:23:08,753
is a real headache.

353
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:11,600
I'm the one with a headache.

354
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:13,620
Same personality.

355
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:17,780
The best three siblings, right?

356
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,400
Do you have any siblings, Kai?

357
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:23,460
I am an only child.

358
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:26,142
My parents divorced

359
00:23:26,158 --> 00:23:27,501
and I live with my father.

360
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:31,640
I can't imagine a lively house.

361
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:35,540
How about you come and meet my siblings?

362
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:38,340
They'll make you forget loneliness.

363
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:41,600
No, I'm not lonely.

364
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:43,305
I've been living alone

365
00:23:43,322 --> 00:23:44,476
since high school.

366
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,640
Is that so?

367
00:23:47,120 --> 00:23:48,573
I stay at my relative's house

368
00:23:48,589 --> 00:23:49,949
near the school.

369
00:23:50,520 --> 00:23:52,440
The commute was super easy.

370
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:58,980
Kai-kun.

371
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:04,000
Don't call me that.

372
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,560
Just ‘Kai' is fine.

373
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,660
The other way feels fake.

374
00:24:11,060 --> 00:24:11,900
Mm.

375
00:24:13,552 --> 00:24:14,540
Kai.

376
00:24:17,900 --> 00:24:18,920
Kai.

377
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,380
Kai is already prepared, yes?

378
00:24:32,360 --> 00:24:33,840
Fuma-san,

379
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,560
they're disappearing.

380
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,640
What should I do?

381
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:51,360
Fuma-san?

382
00:24:52,140 --> 00:24:53,660
No, what should I do?

383
00:24:55,320 --> 00:24:56,140
Huh?

384
00:24:57,080 --> 00:24:58,200
It's nothing.

385
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:01,520
How to draw better?

386
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,740
You have to practice, right?

387
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:08,701
I started drawing when I took

388
00:25:08,709 --> 00:25:10,012
the university entrance exam.

389
00:25:10,037 --> 00:25:12,657
What about before that?

390
00:25:14,420 --> 00:25:16,500
When I started living alone at 15,

391
00:25:16,998 --> 00:25:18,146
I was a bad boy who did

392
00:25:18,162 --> 00:25:19,376
whatever he wanted to do.

393
00:25:19,525 --> 00:25:21,004
Believe it or not, I was a troublemaker

394
00:25:21,029 --> 00:25:22,055
in high school.

395
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:23,908
Did you get that

396
00:25:23,924 --> 00:25:25,798
chest piercing back then?

397
00:25:26,800 --> 00:25:28,840
It's almost closed up.

398
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,380
Ah.

399
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:34,260
Right. Sorry.

400
00:25:34,380 --> 00:25:36,720
I have to go back to work.

401
00:25:37,300 --> 00:25:38,280
Wait.

402
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:43,600
Excuse me, I'm off.

403
00:25:45,780 --> 00:25:47,100
It's tastier

404
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,420
eating with someone else.

405
00:25:53,022 --> 00:25:54,160
Thanks for the meal.

406
00:25:58,740 --> 00:25:59,780
Haa...

407
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:28,000
Hey there, Kai-kun.

408
00:26:30,380 --> 00:26:31,920
It's been a while.

409
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:37,340
You're looking well.

410
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:56,240
(Can you be the sky
at the end of the line?)

411
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:59,280
"Love in The Air -Premonition of Love-"

412
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,440
Don't go.
